---
title: Greek Lamb Steaks with Parsley Butter & Feta Smashed Potato
description: Experience the flavours of the Mediterranean without leaving the house with these juicy lamb steaks that use warm parsley butter to add a delicious herby hit. Our trick of adding feta cheese to lightly smashed potatoes will change the way you prefer your potatoes forever!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/greek-lamb-steaks-5dbe9211.jpg
